The package to provide environment for pbulk
1. bootstrap pkgsrc
2.
 cd /usr/pkgsrc/local-mef/pbulk-addendum
 env PATH=/usr/pkg_bulk/bin:/usr/pkg_bulk/sbin:${PATH} bmake package-install

 By purely personal preference, following package will be installed
   pbulk
   sendmail
   libkver
   zsh
   net-snmp
